### Test Authentication Endpoints
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}
@userId = 123

### Public Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/test-auth/public

### Protected Endpoint (Requires Authentication)
GET {{baseUrl}}/test-auth/protected
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin Only Endpoint (Requires Admin Role)
GET {{baseUrl}}/test-auth/admin-only
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Moderator or Admin Endpoint (Requires Moderator/Admin Role)
GET {{baseUrl}}/test-auth/moderator-or-admin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create User (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/test-auth/create-user
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin-created@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!",
  "firstName": "Admin",
  "lastName": "Created",
  "role": "USER"
}

### Get User Profile by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/test-auth/profile/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin Create User
POST {{baseUrl}}/test-auth/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin-user@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!",
  "firstName": "Admin",
  "lastName": "User",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}